OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPresident sorry for son's  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthreat to invade Kenya     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Uganda's President Yoweri Museveni has 
OL,6, asked Kenyans for "forgiveness" after  
OL,7, his son - a senior military officer -  
OL,8, tweeted about invading their country.  
OL,10,FHis apology came a day after he sacked 
OL,11,FMuhoozi Kainerugaba as commander of the
OL,12,Farmy's land forces.                    
OL,14,FBut Mr Museveni softened the blow by   
OL,15,Fpromoting him to the rank of general,  
OL,16,Fand retaining him as his adviser.      
OL,18,FMr Museveni has long been suspected of 
OL,19,Fgrooming the 48 year old to succeed him
OL,20,Fwhen he eventually steps down.         
